        "院子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾似道上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恼恨裴生理不端，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "调戏我爱妾为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫，贾似道。隐居西湖。可恨裴生，调戏我爱妾慧娘。是我已将慧娘杀死，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把裴生诓进府来，要害他一死！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子上，李慧娘随上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，唤廖应忠进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廖应忠进见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖应忠",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廖应忠上。李慧娘用宝扇搧廖应忠，廖应忠退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖应忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见相爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你三更时分，去至书馆，将裴生杀了见我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖应忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李慧娘搧宝扇，火彩，下。廖应忠随下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾似道",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "裴生呀，裴生！管叫你明枪容易躲，这暗箭最难防。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
