        "裴稚卿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（裴稚卿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谯楼鼓打二更尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李慧娘上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "疾疾走来不消停，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（裴稚卿开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀我妻！往日来早，今日为何来迟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么来早来迟，你的杀身大祸，你还不知么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有什么大祸呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是你非知。可恨那平章老贼。定下暗计，差人前来，要杀你一死！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（裴稚卿惊倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "裴生醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言唬得我三魂不在，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李慧娘去头面，换衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫声贤妻听开怀："
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "裴生休得泪不干，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李慧娘、裴稚卿同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
