    {
      "scene_index": 9,
      "label": "第九场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李慧娘",
        "裴稚卿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李慧娘、裴稚卿同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜将你救出府来。你我夫妻就此分别了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻说哪里话来？你我夫妻逃出相府，正好常常相聚，为何讲说“分别”二字！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看我是一人呐，还是一鬼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你行路有影，说话有声，怎说是鬼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那厢是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李慧娘戴鬼脸。裴稚卿吓倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "裴生醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见贤妻我魂吓掉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由得叫人泪双抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "裴生不要哭号啕，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听我把话说根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老贼杀我赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因此搭救你命一条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从西湖游玩好"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你我结下婚姻事"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻纵然是鬼，我也难以舍得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "本当不回阴曹府，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "阎王怪罪谁承招？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李慧娘",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻们分离在荒郊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二鬼卒拉李慧娘。李慧娘、裴稚卿同哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "裴稚卿",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妻呀！"
        },
